{"tid":31060,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求指點！東京聖誕跨年九日行，23號出發，","createTime":"2016-12-09T12:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T04:44:54.000Z","uid":61658,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2142b84a619e943ab8a7a203382180324cda08b1","tid":31060,"uid":61658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"除左27號晚會住箱根，其他日子都係住新宿，暫時咩行程都未定，小弟第一次去日本，感覺有點徬徨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇完你的名字，好想去朝聖下同買週邊，有無邊啲地方值得去下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外，兒時夢想係去睇高達，預左有一日會去台場，附近有啲咩地方推介？<br />\n<br />\n最後係我同女朋友都好鐘意食野，除左一啲熱門店，有無巴打有必試既誠意推介？<br />\n<br />\n今次旅行儲左好耐錢，望巴打們指點下小弟，萬分感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e57586c2c194e2e190ef9c504fe34d105212d76","tid":31060,"uid":21492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:40:31.000Z","msg":"留名 幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d384f9fdc4cb4b4594b9f922ce6fab2efb32b244","tid":31060,"uid":4158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:43:29.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7da3755871b4028056ceb7e38c23296d4444d5b","tid":31060,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"每個人喜惡唔同, 冇野推介"},{"pid":"d18a21c66eb494e0e1aace1fb1452bc3646e83c0","tid":31060,"uid":5068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:48:59.000Z","msg":"巴打24號到日本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相認下先"},{"pid":"f40922aa518c87d2eed9d84c6c05d5ca78cb53ce","tid":31060,"uid":61658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T20:52:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打24號到日本？<img src=